<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 09:16:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>保时捷名称新的CFO和销售负责人，以恢复绩效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-names-new-cfo-sales-chief-bid-revive-performance-2025-02-26/</link><description>豪华汽车制造商保时捷于周三与两名公司退伍军人一起取代了其首席财务官和销售主管，因为它重新装备了董事会，以期恢复标记绩效和股价较弱。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 09:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-names-new-cfo-sales-chief-bid-revive-performance-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>起亚纠正的课程说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-singles-out-vw-14-billion-tax-dispute-says-kia-corrected-course-2025-02-26/</link><description>法庭文件显示，印度税务机关已将大众汽车列为唯一将其进口赛车进口的汽车制造商在12年内逃避14亿美元的税收，即使竞争对手起亚在被撤职后改变了其行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 09:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-singles-out-vw-14-billion-tax-dispute-says-kia-corrected-course-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>Parexel高管说，印度正处于成为临床试验中心的边缘。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/india-verge-becoming-clinical-trials-hub-parexel-executive-says-2025-02-26/</link><description>合同研究公司Parexel的高管Parexel在周三对路透社表示，印度已准备好作为早期临床试验的替代地点，以帮助减轻俄罗斯 - 乌克兰战争等干扰的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 08:39:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/india-verge-becoming-clinical-trials-hub-parexel-executive-says-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>食品集团达能（Danone）在2024年强劲的销售和现金绩效之后自信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/food-group-danone-confident-after-strong-2024-sales-cash-performance-2025-02-26/</link><description>达能（Danone）周三表示，它在将2024年的销售额和现金超过分析师的期望之上发出后，在其复兴计划的下一个领域开始了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 06:36:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/food-group-danone-confident-after-strong-2024-sales-cash-performance-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：CICC与Galaxy Securities合并以组成中国的第三级经纪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/cicc-merge-with-galaxy-securities-form-chinas-no3-brokerage-say-sources-2025-02-26/</link><description>五个消息来源说，国际国际国际资本公司（CICC）将与其同行中国银河证券合并，这项交易将创建该国的第三大经纪公司，资产为1930亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 06:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/cicc-merge-with-galaxy-securities-form-chinas-no3-brokerage-say-sources-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国在台湾海岸上举行“射击”演习，誓言“统一”推动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-flags-chinas-shooting-drills-off-southwest-coast-2025-02-26/</link><description>台北被描述为挑衅和危险的举动，周三在台湾西南海岸举行了“射击训练”，而中国高级领导人誓言将岛屿置于北京的控制之下。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 06:25:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-flags-chinas-shooting-drills-off-southwest-coast-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>Brewer AB Inbev的利润增长，但中国啤酒的销售动摇了</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brewer-ab-inbevs-q4-profits-beat-expectations-2025-02-26/</link><description>啤酒巨头Anheuser-Busch Inbev周三报告说，预测的第四季度利润，即使中国啤酒市场的放缓也拖延了数量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 06:16:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brewer-ab-inbevs-q4-profits-beat-expectations-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜的金正日呼吁建立现代军队为战争做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-calls-building-modern-army-brace-war-2025-02-26/</link><description>朝鲜领导人金正恩（Kim Jong Un）呼吁建立一支强大的现代军队，以应对军事学院期间的任何战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 05:57:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-calls-building-modern-army-brace-war-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国比赛监管机构与阿里巴巴，梅赛德斯 - 奔驰进行了会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-competition-regulator-holds-talks-with-alibaba-mercedes-benz-2025-02-26/</link><description>国家监管局（SAMR）周三在一份声明中说，中国市场监管机构与七家公司的高管举行了与七家公司的高管进行公平竞争研讨会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 04:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-competition-regulator-holds-talks-with-alibaba-mercedes-benz-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>库克群岛总理在中国公约上幸存下来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cook-islands-pm-survives-no-confidence-vote-over-china-pact-2025-02-26/</link><description>库克群岛总理马克·布朗（Mark Brown）周三幸存下来，对反对派对他与中国达成的交易造成的交易无信心，这与新西兰的关系紧张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 03:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cook-islands-pm-survives-no-confidence-vote-over-china-pact-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>达利安铁矿石在中国钢出口前景上延伸了连胜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/iron-ore-dips-chinese-steel-export-concerns-us-sino-trade-tensions-2025-02-26/</link><description>铁矿石期货的价格在周三连续第三次会议上削弱了中国和中国顶级消费者之间的贸易紧张局势，这一幅度降低了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 03:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/iron-ore-dips-chinese-steel-export-concerns-us-sino-trade-tensions-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>香港削减10,000名公务员工作，推动AI抗拒赤字</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-expects-gdp-growth-2-3-2025-2025-02-26/</link><description>香港的目标是通过削减10,000个公务员工作的工作来削减支出，以遏制赤字的增加，并计划在全球经济不确定性，地缘政治紧张局势和薄弱房地产市场中脱颖而出时，AI大力推动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 03:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-expects-gdp-growth-2-3-2025-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，台湾试图将芯片行业赠送给我们</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-says-taiwan-seeks-give-away-chip-industry-us-2025-02-26/</link><description>中国表示，台湾正在寻求将岛上的半导体行业赠送给美国，作为“纪念品”，并利用它来寻求华盛顿的政治支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 03:11:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-says-taiwan-seeks-give-away-chip-industry-us-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国从哪里得到铜？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/where-does-us-get-its-copper-2025-02-26/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周二下令对铜进口的可能关税进行调查，以重建美国生产对电动汽车，军事硬件，半导体和广泛消费品的金属生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 02:50:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/where-does-us-get-its-copper-2025-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，台湾“操纵”海底电缆切割事件在事实清楚之前</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-manipulating-undersea-cable-cutting-before-facts-clear-2025-02-26/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，台湾正在“操纵”中国可能参与海底通信电缆的最新切断，称该岛在事实很明显之前正在施放急诊。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 02:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-manipulating-undersea-cable-cutting-before-facts-clear-2025-02-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>